<sect2 id="Slider"><title>Slider</title>
<para>A slider with slid and knob</para>
<para>
<code>A slider is used to let user specifying a value by scrolling.</code>
</para>
<para>
<code>A slider accepts a range of value starting from 0 to 100. You could change the maximal</code>
</para>
<para>
<code>allowed value by the </code>
<code>maxpos</code>
<code> property.</code>
</para>
<para>
<graphic fileref="images/Slider.png"/>
</para>
<programlisting>&lt;slider id="slider" /&gt;&#13;&lt;slider curpos=”1” maxpos=”20” /&gt;&#13;</programlisting><sect3><title>Class Name</title>
<para>
<code>org.zkoss.zul.Slider</code> </para></sect3><sect3><title>Supported Child Components</title>
